sql_query.sql: SELECT "api_chatmessage"."id", "api_chatmessage"."user_id", "api_chatmessage"."sender_id", "api_chatmessage"."reciever_id", "api_chatmessage"."message", "api_chatmessage"."is_read", "api_chatmessage"."date", "api_user"."id", "api_user"."password", "api_user"."last_login", "api_user"."is_superuser", "api_user"."first_name", "api_user"."last_name", "api_user"."is_staff", "api_user"."is_active", "api_user"."date_joined", "api_user"."username", "api_user"."email", T3."id", T3."password", T3."last_login", T3."is_superuser", T3."first_name", T3."last_name", T3."is_staff", T3."is_active", T3."date_joined", T3."username", T3."email", T4."id", T4."password", T4."last_login", T4."is_superuser", T4."first_name", T4."last_name", T4."is_staff", T4."is_active", T4."date_joined", T4."username", T4."email" FROM "api_chatmessage" INNER JOIN "api_user" ON ("api_chatmessage"."user_id" = "api_user"."id") INNER JOIN "api_user" T3 ON ("api_chatmessage"."sender_id" = T3."id") INNER JOIN "api_user" T4 ON ("api_chatmessage"."reciever_id" = T4."id") ORDER BY "api_chatmessage"."id" DESC
